                <h5 class="text-montserrat-bold">MySQL Versi 5.6</h5>
                <p class="text-roboto">Nikmati MySQL versi terbaru, tercepat dan kaya akan fitur</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 p-4 text-center">
                <img class="img-fluid mb-4" width="70" src="assets/svg/icon%20PHP%20Hosting_CPanel.svg"
                    title="cpanel" />
                <h5 class="text-montserrat-bold">Panel Hosting cPanel</h5>
                <p class="text-roboto">Kelola website dengan panel canggih yang familiar di hati Anda.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 p-4 text-center">
                <img class="img-fluid mb-4" width="70" src="assets/svg/icon%20PHP%20Hosting_garansi%20uptime.svg"
                    title="garansi uptime 99%" />
                <h5 class="text-montserrat-bold">Garansi Uptime 99.9%</h5>
                <p class="text-roboto">Data center yang mendukung kelangsungan website Anda 24/7.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 p-4 text-center">
                <img class="img-fluid mb-4" width="70" src="assets/svg/icon%20PHP%20Hosting_InnoDB.svg"
                    title="unlimited innodb" />
                <h5 class="text-montserrat-bold">Database InnoDB Unlimited</h5>
                <p class="text-roboto">Jumlah dan ukuran database yang tumbuh sesuai kebutuhan Anda.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 p-4 text-center">
                <img class="img-fluid mb-4" width="70" src="assets/svg/icon%20PHP%20Hosting_My%20SQL%20remote.svg"
                    title="wildcard remote mysql" />
                <h5 class="text-montserrat-bold">Wildcard Remote MySQL</h5>
                <p class="text-roboto">Mendukung s/d 25 max_user_connections dan 100 max_connections.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="divider my-4"></div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                <h3 class="mb-4">Mendukung Penuh Framework Laravel</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 my-auto mb-5 px-4 mb-lg-auto">
                <p class="mb-4">Tak perlu menggunakan dedicated server ataupun VPS yang mahal. Layanan PHP hosting murah
                    kami mendukung penuh framework favorit Anda</p>
                <p class="mb-2 text-roboto"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill green-icon"></i> &nbsp; Install Laravel
                    <span class="text-roboto-bold">1
                        klik</span> dengan Softaculous Installer.
                </p>
                <p class="mb-2 text-roboto"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill green-icon"></i> &nbsp; Mendukung ekstensi
                    <span class="text-roboto-bold">PHP MCrypt, phar, mbstring, json,</span> dan <span
                        class="text-roboto-bold">fileinfo.</span>
                </p>
                <p class="mb-4 text-roboto"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill green-icon"></i> &nbsp; Tersedia
                    <span class="text-roboto-bold">Composer</span> dan <span class="text-roboto-bold">SSH</span> untuk
                    menginstal packages pilihan Anda.
                </p>
                <p class="mb-4 text-roboto fs-12">Nb. Composer dan SSH hanya tersedia pada paket Personal dan
                    Bisnis</p>

                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary rounded-25 text-montserrat-bold py-2 px-4">Pilih Hosting
                    Anda</button>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 px-4 my-auto">
                <img class="img-fluid" width="100%"
                    src="assets/svg/illustration%20banner%20support%20laravel%20hosting.svg" alt="mbstring json phar" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section><!-- End About Section -->
<hr class="divider">
